      "content": "but that's the thing... the quiet isn't just something i'm \"wearing.\" it's everything. i look at his side of the bed and it's like there's a hole in the universe. i feel like i'm just dragging this empty body through the days because i have to, but there's no reason to actually be here. it's like i'm already gone.",
