      "content": "it feels like i'm just waiting for something to happen. but nothing does. i'm just existing in this void, and every morning i wake up and realize i'm still here, still alone, and it's just so exhausting. it feels like staying is just a way of prolonging the pain. wouldn't it just be easier to finally be at peace?",
